QuestData.Title: Poison Paralysis
QuestData.Description: There are others from the caravan that have gone missing.$b$bMy guess is they have been taken into Blademoon Bloom by the botani.$b$bYou have to rescue them, $n. You are our only hope.$b$bHere, take some of this elixir I just made, chances are you will need it.
QuestData.RewardText: I can never repay you for all you have done here today, $n.$b$bI am truly in your debt.
